---

<section class="bg-primary py-stack-lg">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-margin-mobile text-center">
    <h2 class="font-display-lg text-headline-md text-on-primary mb-6">¿Desea recibir nuestras crónicas mensuales?</h2>
    <p class="font-body-lg text-on-primary/70 mb-stack-sm">Una selección curada de hallazgos, sabores y silencios de Nicaragua, directamente en su correo.</p>
    <form class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 mt-8">
      <input
        type="email"
        placeholder="Su correo electrónico"
        class="flex-grow bg-white/5 border-white/20 text-on-primary font-body-md px-6 py-4 focus:ring-0 focus:border-secondary outline-none placeholder:text-white/30"
      />
      <button
        type="submit"
        class="bg-secondary text-white px-10 py-4 font-label-caps text-label-caps tracking-widest hover:brightness-110 transition-all uppercase"
      >
        Suscribirse
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>
